        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-04-07T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-04-07T00:00:00-05:00" n="150" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d150">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">840.20/4–749</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the <gloss type="from">Secretary of
                            State</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">President</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-04-07">April 7,
                            1949</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Memorandum for the President</hi>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">Subject: North Atlantic Treaty</p>
                <p>I attach my report on the North Atlantic Treaty<note n="1" xml:id="d150fn1">For
                        text of report, dated April 7, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, April 24, 1949, p. 532.</note> together with a draft
                    message to the Senate<note n="2" xml:id="d150fn2">For text of final version,
                        dated April 12, see <hi rend="italic">ibid.</hi>, May 8, 1949, p.
                        599.</note> for your consideration and transmission to the Senate if you
                    approve.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dean Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
